Class JSON

  • java.lang.Object
    • no.ntnu.imt3281.movieExplorer.JSON

  • public class JSON
extends java.lang.Object
    JSON object has a list capable of holding objects of type JSON the structure allows it to either hold a instance of JSONObject, in which the key and value field is used, or a JSONArray, in which the obj and key field is used.
